{"tid":1559180,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急! 推到上報! 要HA 交代!! HAIT 高層圖隱瞞遭黑客入侵事件, 7百萬港人資料恐洩漏","createTime":"2019-09-10T16:46:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T07:11:37.000Z","uid":127748,"like":107,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":103,"replies":[{"pid":"7276fe03d925ce6339463a5a7569b49bffc6e0f4","tid":1559180,"uid":127748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:46:43.000Z","msg":"HA Secrets<br />\n30分鐘 &middot; <br />\n#9276 [fact checked and Emergency action required !]<br />\n<br />\nCHANGE CMS PASSWORD NOW !<br />\n<br />\n&quot;[HAIT 高層圖隱瞞遭黑客入侵事件, 7百萬港人資料恐洩漏]<br />\n<br />\n本人是HAIT 的員工, 2019/09/06 收工後 ,負責儲存HA 員工的CORP ID 認證的一台伺服器, ldaps://<a href=\"http://ldapscorp.server.ha.org.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fldapscorp.server.ha.org.hk&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRegZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=f6127124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ldapscorp.server.ha.org.hk</a>:XXX 遭受到黑客攻擊而一度未能連線. 由於IT 高層擔心黑客取得員工的CORP ID 進行非法存取/破壞, 隨即在kitec 6/F 的HAIT 辦公室內的Meeting Room D, 成立了一個名為Cyber Incident Response Team 的小組, 房內設有一名IT 同事及一台電腦, 奉命協助所有同事更改CORP ID 及 Internet Account 的密碼，可見事態嚴重之程度. 正常嚟講需要alert 各自部門 Health checking 唔係IT department 可以單獨處理<br />\n無公佈係好唔正常<br />\n<br />\n可惜整個安排, 沒有任何高層或小組作出任何回應/解釋/澄清事情的始末, 連一封email 都沒有... 同事間只能口耳相傳. 有理由相信, HAIT高層企圖淡化事件, 做法令人關注.<br />\n<br />\n今日 1816 個email 係 09/02 , 係另一單<br />\n<br />\n#9277<br />\nmsg on 9 sept afternoon : CMS were hacked 8 Sept 2019 night (CMS = clinical management system<br />\n, this is a system to store all patience records)<br />\n<br />\nAdmin: 即係懷疑 HA 默許 6/9 取得密碼既人係8/9 access 入CMS ? 包括QEH 眼爆少女既Medical report.<br />\n寫report 果幾位眼科同事望下自己d 野有冇比人改到啦.<br />\nupdate: 理論上, CMS 被改係有Foot print 既...... 不過哩...... 依個時候?"},{"pid":"26325574bc562b54e37cf04b7d08cb3d18e66d0a","tid":1559180,"uid":127748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:47:49.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b7de4b807811aba9d06c15dab2199fd351df9dd2","tid":1559180,"uid":127748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:49:52.000Z","msg":"推 雖然任何刪改都會係CMS有記錄 但係警方聲稱話囉左爆眼少女既REPORT既時候有呢D事 唔可以比佢當無事"},{"pid":"8be8ac1eb3d0d2870853addad005ca29ab66e7af","tid":1559180,"uid":127748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:50:39.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f36be2bdef4dd739da4c17d34267a8fdaaf219e9","tid":1559180,"uid":128388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:51:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">915 12點英領 3點民陣</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"6469a6c58b15f33a8b9c9f6510316852ece9ce47","tid":1559180,"uid":127748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:51:33.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"875d8c5daf7e6cc540216df6b176039114e19d65","tid":1559180,"uid":115740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:51:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da018b9ecbbf1021cfb52b37a30256aad01c91a2","tid":1559180,"uid":127748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:52:38.000Z","msg":"自推 請媒體報道 及要求HA 交代事件"},{"pid":"f0fcf4f0da51edf2c975535ecabfd0a61d39ae37","tid":1559180,"uid":30836,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:53:42.000Z","msg":"係真<br />\n有朋友喺HA做緊<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"7b7cfa7014b1e5c62b5cf6678bcaa710cc89fbb4","tid":1559180,"uid":127748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:54:27.000Z","msg":"自推 請媒體報道 及要求HA 交代事件"},{"pid":"53a9e15f67b5c83867ae4ac96d089c11fc826cc1","tid":1559180,"uid":196450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:54:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8417ea46a06fdb4050d55d5d44ac720714bec9bb","tid":1559180,"uid":215717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:55:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f45290